  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You are even more deadly in magical darkness.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Improved Unarmed Strike, Intimidate 1 rank, ability to create magical darkness.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While fighting within an area of magical darkness, you gain a +2 bonus on damage rolls with unarmed strikes, or a +4 bonus against opponents that are shaken, frightened, or panicked. You also gain a +2 morale bonus on Acrobatics and Intimidate checks.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When fighting in an area of magical darkness, you can spend up to 5 stamina points to increase the bonus granted by this feat on one damage roll by double the number of stamina points you spent.",
